							                    <h2 class="">The Huntington Rose Garden Tea Room</h2>
				
				<div class="slide-key image-holder gallery-image-holder credit-image-wrap  "
					 					data-slide-num="10"
					data-post-id="1575462"

					>
											
																					<picture>
																	<source
										media="(min-width: 429px)"
										data-srcset="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/the-huntington-rose-garden-tea-room-1714734903.webp"
										type="image/webp">
									<source
										media="(max-width: 428px)"
										data-srcset="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/the-huntington-rose-garden-tea-room-1714734903.sm.webp"
										type="image/webp">
																<img class="gallery-image lazyload " src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNkYAAAAAYAAjCB0C8AAAAASUVORK5CYII="
									data-lazy-src="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/the-huntington-rose-garden-tea-room-1714734903.jpg" data-slide-url="https://www.tastingtable.com/1575462/best-afternoon-tea-los-angeles/slide/the-huntington-rose-garden-tea-room/"
									data-post-id="1575462"
									data-slide-num="10"
									data-slide-title="The 15 Best Afternoon Teas In Los Angeles, According To A Local: The Huntington Rose Garden Tea Room"
																		width="780" height="438"
									alt="Friends having tea and snacks">
							</picture>
																				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/B782jayBBUs/" target="_blank"><span class="gallery-image-credit">rosegardentearoom/Instagram</span></a></a>									</div>

				
				<div class="columns-holder ">
                    					<p>
<p dir="ltr">Technically located in San Marino, The Huntington Rose Garden Tea Room is an iconic establishment that is a must-try for tea lovers. Sit outside on the picturesque patio as you take in the peaceful sounds of trickling fountains and chirping birds while enjoying a piping-hot cup of tea. The tea room is open every day except Tuesdays, providing more flexibility for patrons with a more restrictive schedule on the weekends. Saturdays and Sundays, the tea room is open 10:30 a.m. to 5 p.m., while Monday, Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday service goes from 11 a.m. to 4 p.m.</p>
<div class="google-ad-placeholder between-p" data-ad-height="any" data-ad-width="any" data-ad-pos="between-p"></div>
<p dir="ltr">Enjoy the traditional tea for $62 per person ($28 per child), or the Huntington tea for $75 per person. In addition to a glass of bubbles, the pricier Huntington tea includes a poached Maine lobster roll and a special bonbon. Those who follow a plant-based diet will be pleased to find a vegan tea menu, and there is also a gluten-free option for those with gluten intolerance or allergies. Just keep in mind that the Huntington Tea Room is situated within the larger rose garden and botanical garden, so you need to buy a ticket to enter. Admission is $29, but the gardens are breathtaking and well worth perusing before or after your afternoon tea.</p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="https://huntington.org/tea-room" target="_blank">www.huntington.org/tea-room</a></p>
<p dir="ltr">(626) 405-3453</p>
<p dir="ltr">1151 Oxford Rd, San Marino, CA 91108</p>
<div class="google-ad-placeholder between-p" data-ad-height="any" data-ad-width="any" data-ad-pos="between-p"></div>
</p>
					
									</div>
					</div>

    <div class="news-article   ">
			

							                    <h2 class="">The London West Hollywood</h2>
				
				<div class="slide-key image-holder gallery-image-holder credit-image-wrap  "
					 					data-slide-num="11"
					data-post-id="1575462"

					>
											
																					<picture>
																	<source
										media="(min-width: 429px)"
