							                    <h2 class="">Rendezvous Court</h2>
				
				<div class="slide-key image-holder gallery-image-holder credit-image-wrap  "
					 					data-slide-num="12"
					data-post-id="1575462"

					>
											
																					<picture>
																	<source
										media="(min-width: 429px)"
										data-srcset="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/rendezvous-court-1714734903.webp"
										type="image/webp">
									<source
										media="(max-width: 428px)"
										data-srcset="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/rendezvous-court-1714734903.sm.webp"
										type="image/webp">
																<img class="gallery-image lazyload " src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNkYAAAAAYAAjCB0C8AAAAASUVORK5CYII="
									data-lazy-src="https://www.tastingtable.com/img/gallery/the-15-best-afternoon-teas-in-los-angeles-according-to-a-local/rendezvous-court-1714734903.jpg" data-slide-url="https://www.tastingtable.com/1575462/best-afternoon-tea-los-angeles/slide/rendezvous-court/"
									data-post-id="1575462"
									data-slide-num="12"
									data-slide-title="The 15 Best Afternoon Teas In Los Angeles, According To A Local: Rendezvous Court"
																		width="780" height="438"
									alt="Woman pouring tea near snacks">
							</picture>
																				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C17yA2jNItJ/" target="_blank"><span class="gallery-image-credit">thebiltmorela/Instagram</span></a></a>									</div>

				
				<div class="columns-holder ">
                    					<p>
<p dir="ltr">Located within the Biltmore Los Angeles, the Rendezvous Court sets the scene for one of the most luxurious and classy afternoon teas in LA. Guests can sit around the fairytale decor and trickling rose marble fountain as they sip on hot herbal blends and nibble on quaint finger foods. The show-stopping and grandiose architecture is unlike any other hotel in the city, boasting a more European-style setting that is perfect for afternoon tea. Tea is served on Saturdays between 2 p.m. and 5 p.m. and costs $75 per person.</p>
<div class="google-ad-placeholder between-p" data-ad-height="any" data-ad-width="any" data-ad-pos="between-p"></div>
<p dir="ltr">In addition to the selection of teas and pastries, a glass of Champagne is also included in the price, allowing guests to sip on some bubbles without having to pay the extra price that most afternoon tea experiences require. Finger sandwiches include <a href="https://www.tastingtable.com/1170838/how-prue-leith-updated-queen-elizabeths-classic-coronation-chicken/" target="_blank">British favorites like coronation chicken</a> and ham with tomato chutney, as well as surprising, fanciful foods like an egg salad sandwich with Siberian Reserve caviar. From rose-flavored macarons to pistachio and almond cakes, the sweets are almost too pretty eat, so be sure to snap a photo of your food and floral tea set before digging.</p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.millenniumhotels.com/en/los-angeles/millennium-biltmore-hotel-los-angeles/rendezvous-court-cafe/" target="_blank">www.millenniumhotels.com/en/los-angeles/millennium-biltmore-hotel-los-angeles/rendezvous-court-cafe</a></p>
<p dir="ltr">(213) 612-1562</p>
<div class="google-ad-placeholder between-p" data-ad-height="any" data-ad-width="any" data-ad-pos="between-p"></div>
<p dir="ltr">506 S Grand Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90071</p>
</p>
					
									</div>
					</div>

    <div class="news-article   ">
			

